{"tid":1518194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【8.30 大搜捕】前港大學生會會長孫曉嵐被捕　涉進入立法會會議廳","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:03:20.000Z","uid":38954,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45ed85741e7bd754846791e816c15e9094eefe28","tid":1518194,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"前港大學生會會長孫曉嵐透過友人透露，昨日清晨，有警察上門以涉嫌「串謀摧毀及損壞財產」與「進入或逗留會議廳範圍」拘捕，並出示搜查令，但由於當時孫曉嵐不在家，她今日下午兩時半已由律師陪同到灣仔警察總部。<br />\n<br />\n孫曉嵐個人 fb 戶口今午公布消息，並指由「友人代出」，帖文引述孫曉嵐籲友好不必擔心，並多關注「連日警方大搜捕中其他被捕義士」。"},{"pid":"9ee64170d1e8b5a03c3a2ec03efcdf9de83b7c56","tid":1518194,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUis4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=2b1d6bdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUis4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=421d3e73\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUis4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=b51dd3b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"3ccacd5274d8b3e116f74e689b343bb2b18d037c","tid":1518194,"uid":247699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUis4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=cd8defd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb010e556e406a79488806c384227a4dc76035a","tid":1518194,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d894ee02182ec7377483a840e7ebce0281572f7a","tid":1518194,"uid":235796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5cb6885d457f084d81909885735cf23b3946c3df","tid":1518194,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"7b901ee516fcf2130f37e3d6eb299b1e3d5a1812","tid":1518194,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"政府你想對話？對你老味啊"},{"pid":"08034a5b7aba759cd1dd3006437d1a884b405b09","tid":1518194,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b901ee516fcf2130f37e3d6eb299b1e3d5a1812","tid":1518194,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"政府你想對話？對你老味啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"捉哂先傾"},{"pid":"cc3ea4913bc7522bd762